and have fun like this?

524
00:39:03,150 --> 00:39:05,510
We will go on vacation somewhere else.

525
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,720
Where?

526
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:09,050
Somewhere more fun than the flying pavilion?

527
00:39:09,050 --> 00:39:11,900
Yes. You'll see.

528
00:39:11,900 --> 00:39:15,030
 Even though you turned me
into an animal and keep petting me, 

529
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:18,030
 you did it to protect me. 

530
00:39:18,030 --> 00:39:21,530
 Sima Jiao, I guess
you're not completely heartless after all. 

531
00:39:34,010 --> 00:39:35,530
What's wrong with these puppet servants?

532
00:39:35,530 --> 00:39:36,780
Are they broken?

533
00:39:36,780 --> 00:39:41,850
These puppet servants are all eyes for that old fool, Shi Qian Lv.

534
00:39:41,850 --> 00:39:43,720
You said it so calmly.

535
00:39:43,720 --> 00:39:46,380
You knew from the start, didn't you?

536
00:39:47,630 --> 00:39:50,110
If I hadn't left him a few flaws to find,

537
00:39:50,110 --> 00:39:53,090
how else would he have lowered his guard?

538
00:39:54,140 --> 00:39:55,780
How long will we be gone?

539
00:39:55,780 --> 00:39:58,070
Will people find out?

540
