the way Ting Yan did. 

543
00:40:08,450 --> 00:40:10,740
 Don't mention that dead woman again. 

544
00:40:10,740 --> 00:40:13,340
 Have you found who spread the news
about Liao Ting Yan? 

545
00:40:13,340 --> 00:40:14,870
 Yes. 

546
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:17,880
 It was An Xue from Three Saints Mountain. 

547
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:20,700
 She held a grudge against Ting Yan, 

548
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:25,450
 so she must have spread the news
to take revenge. 

549
00:40:25,450 --> 00:40:29,810
 But she's already dead, so I couldn't get anything out of her. 

550
00:40:29,810 --> 00:40:31,670
Sima Jiao.

